R@20, 1.0% on SGCLS-R@20 and 1.0% on SGDET-
R@20 for the strategy With Constraint, which shows that
STTran performs better than image-based baselines in pre-
dicting the most important relationships between an object
pair. Our model also has excellent performance (see Table
2): 1.9% on PredCLS-R@20, 1.5% on SGCLS-R@20 and
0.6% improvement on SGDET-R@20 for Semi Constraint
that allows multiple relationships between a subject-object
pair. For No Constraint, STTran outperforms other meth-
